---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Admissions — Mt Cedar British International School"
  description="Admissions for the 2026/2027 session are open at Mt Cedar British International School, Benin City, across Early Years, Primary and Secondary. See how to apply."
  active="admissions"
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">Admissions 2026 / 2027</p>
    <h1>Come and see where your child will grow.</h1>
    <p>Applications are open across Early Years, Primary and Secondary. Arrange a visit, meet our teachers, and feel the Mt Cedar difference in person.</p>
    <div class="cta" style="margin-top:1.8rem">
      <a class="btn btn-gold btn-lg" href="/contact">Start an Enquiry <span class="arr">→</span></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg" href="tel:09043729659">Call 0904 372 9659</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head"><p class="eyebrow">How to Apply</p><h2>Three simple steps to a place.</h2><p>We keep admissions warm and personal. Here is how the journey usually goes.</p></div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <h3>Enquire</h3>
        <p>Send us a message or give us a call with your child’s age and the stage you’re interested in. We’ll answer your questions and share what’s available.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>Visit</h3>
        <p>Come and tour the school, meet our teachers and see our classrooms. It’s the best way to know whether Mt Cedar is right for your family.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>Enrol</h3>
        <p>Complete the application, and we’ll guide you through assessment and registration so your child is ready to start with confidence.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="background:var(--ivory-2)">
  <div class="wrap two-col">
    <div class="lead-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Good to Know</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.7rem,3vw,2.3rem);margin:.5rem 0 1.1rem">What to expect.</h2>
      <p><strong>Stages open:</strong> Early Years (ages 2–5), Primary (ages 5–11) and Secondary (ages 11–16).</p>
      <p><strong>Session:</strong> Enrolment for the 2026/2027 academic session is now open across all stages.</p>
      <p><strong>Class sizes:</strong> We keep classes small and focused, so places in each year group are limited — early enquiries are encouraged.</p>
      <p><strong>What to bring to a visit:</strong> just yourselves. We’ll walk you through everything else in person.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cform" style="align-self:start">
      <h3 style="font-family:var(--display);font-size:1.4rem;margin:0 0 .3rem">Ready to begin?</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 1.2rem;font-size:.98rem">Reach us directly and we’ll get straight back to you.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-cedar" style="width:100%;margin-bottom:.7rem" href="mailto:mtcedarbritishinternationalsch@gmail.com?subject=Admissions%20Enquiry">Email an Enquiry</a>
      <a class="btn btn-outline" style="width:100%" href="tel:08056733071">Call 0805 673 3071</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="band">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--gold-bright)">We’d love to meet you</p>
    <h2>Book a visit to Mt Cedar.</h2>
    <p>See the classrooms, meet the teachers, and picture your child here. We’ll make time for you.</p>
    <div class="cta">
      <a class="btn btn-gold btn-lg" href="/contact">Arrange a Visit <span class="arr">→</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
